Before baubeginn he "of the city, the appropriate baugenehmigung but made him information about the planned reconstruction were so vague that the stadtväter two years later in the completion of were appalled by the result, so much so that they help demanded.
The ratsherren met with, among other things, to ensure that the construction of his pillars, even in the public pavement intervention.
