On the other hand, he said that China would not change its goals, but would work together with the international community in this matter.
He said that the Chinese unterteile strategy on climate change in four aspects: dialogue, capacity building, construction of institutions and support of pilotprogrammen.
We have made progress in all aspects, including the adoption of a new energiegesetzes in the last year, which delivers the targets for reduction of emissions of gases, he said.
On the other hand, he stressed that in China, the authorities of the States with those of zentralstaats and the communities would have worked together to the targets for the energy conservation, an efficient use of energy and the reduction of emissions.
